"title": "8321: perfection, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8321: perfection, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The state of being whole, complete or without defect in any way.</p>\n<h2>Only God is absolutely perfect</h2>\n<h3>In his nature and character</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:14\">ECC 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a></p>\n<h3>In his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7\">PSA 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:8-Prov8:9\">PRO 8:8–8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5\">PRO 30:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">JAS 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>In his morality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:26-2Sam22:27\">2SA 22:26–22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:17\">JOB 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>In his will and providence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31\">2SA 22:31</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In his knowledge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:16\">JOB 37:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:4\">PSA 139:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13-Isa40:14\">ISA 40:13–40:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:13\">HEB 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>In his faithfulness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:1\">ISA 25:1</a></p>\n<h2>God's perfect creation</h2>\n<h3>In its original condition</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1-Gen2:2\">GEN 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:10\">GEN 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:12\">GEN 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:18\">GEN 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:21\">GEN 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:25\">GEN 1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:25-Isa40:26\">ISA 40:25–40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:3\">HEB 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>The coming new creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:10\">1CO 13:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:5\">REV 21:1–21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:5\">REV 22:1–22:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's perfect self-revelation in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>The moral perfection of Jesus Christ as God's Son</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26\">HEB 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:5\">1JN 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>The perfect sacrifice of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:21\">LEV 22:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:2\">NUM 19:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:19</a></p>",
